{{!
  @template block_rss_plus/item

  RSS Plus RSS item template

  The purpose of this template is to render a RSS item

  Classes required for JS:
  * none
  
  Data attributes required for JS:
  * none

  Context variables required for this template
  * link String URL of the RSS item
  * title String Title of the RSS item
  * thumbnails Array of Strings URL to thumbnail
  * description String a summary of the RSS item

  Example context (json):
  {
    "link": "http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-34453739",
    "title": "Russia violation of Turkish airspace 'no accident'"
    "thumbnails": [
      "http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/660/_85941173_85941172.jpg"
    ],
    "description": "Russia's violation of Turkish airspace over the weekend..."
  }
}}
<li>
    <div class="rsslink">
        <a href="{{link}}" onclick="this.target='_blank'">{{title}}</a>
    </div>
    <div class="rssimage">
    {{#thumbnails}}
        <img src="{{.}}" />
    {{/thumbnails}}
    </div>
    <div class="rssdescription">{{description}}</div>
</li>
